Create data frame for the mosaic:

xlim <- c(0, 10)
ylim <- c(0, 10)

# Create a data frame with the spots for tiles
container <- expand.grid(x = seq(xlim[1], xlim[2], 1),
                         y = seq(ylim[1], ylim[2], 1)) %>%
  mutate(tiles = case_when(x <= 2 | x >= 8 ~ "dl", 
                           x > 2 & x <8 ~ "dr"))
st_truchet_ss(df = container) %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_sf()
